Fix for /usr/bin/python missing on Monterey 12.3+:
mkdir mnt
sudo mount_apfs system_partition mnt
cd mnt/usr/bin
sudo ln -s python3 python
cd ../../..
sudo bless --mount mnt --create-snapshot --bootefi
sudo reboot
NOTE: System partition is not an APFS snapshot
